HomeAway data 01

Radoslaw Panczak

10 September, 2019

1 Summary

This is an overview of raw HomeAway dataset.

Separate preparation is done for ha (properties) and ham (monthly) datasets.

2 Properties

2.1 General

  • All variable names were converted to lower caps
  • Dots/gaps in the names were replaced by single underscores.
  • Completely empty variables (Zipcode and Metropolitan_Statistical_Area) were dropped.
  • Variable Country was droped.
  • Data was spatially linked to ABS geography with SA1 and above level variables added.

Raw dataset consists of 83297 records of Austrlian Airbnb properties as scraped by Airdna.

Dataset consists of 46 variables:

4 Monthly

Raw dataset consists of 1082116 records of ham statistics of Austrlian Airbnb properties scraped by Airdna. ## General

  • Dotsin the names were replaced by (single) underscores.
  • Completely empty variables (Zipcode and Metropolitan_Statistical_Area) were dropped.
  • Variable Country was droped.
  • Variables State, City and Neighborhood were droped (no clue how assigned; will be added from ABS data linked spatially by coordinates)

Dataset consists of 1082116 records in 16 variables:

##  [1] "property_id"            "property_manager_id"   
##  [3] "property_type"          "bedrooms"              
##  [5] "reporting_month"        "occupancy_rate"

## [13] "latitude"               "longitude"             
## [15] "active"                 "scraped_during_month"
